PrecisAuthority for the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION to lease some 1.699 hectares of vacant land to the CORPORATION OF THE CITY OF GLOUCESTER, for a fixed term of twenty-five (25) years, the land in question being situate on Innes Road at the Blackburn By-pass, Gloucester, Ontario, which is to be used as a site for a municipal fire hall and civic training centre.
